{"tid":2499720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「譽宴」涉迫員工打針 觀塘分店經理：已自願打兩針疫苗，是為了國家","createTime":"2021-04-22T05:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T08:37:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11e38bce2a362216003018edb3454e14806c580d","tid":2499720,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"【「譽宴」涉迫員工打針　職工盟赴觀塘分店抗議】<br />\n【經理：已自願打兩針疫苗，是為了國家、為香港、為飯碗、為老闆﹗】<br />\n<br />\n早前連鎖酒家「譽宴」集團被爆出內部文件，要求員工必需接種疫苗，否則於下周四（29 日）起則要停工。職工盟、飲食及酒店業職工總會今（22 日）到其觀塘分店抗議，要求集團收回決定。<br />\n<br />\n一名姓葉分店經理阻止眾人叫口號及展示橫額，經理又自稱，已自願接種兩劑疫苗，「我哋咁做法都係為國家、為香港、為自己飯碗、為老闆」，故不覺得有問題，惟被在場人士質疑「為飯碗」難稱作自願。<br />\n<br />\n經理一度報警，7 至 8 名警員到場調停。職工盟成員交下請願信予經理，要求譽宴集團主席張家豪交代，其後和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n譽宴集團主席張家豪早前曾回應一事，指內部文件中「停工」一詞只是「用住先」，實際如何安排不接種疫苗的員工，仍在考慮中。<br />\n<br />\n稍後有詳細報道"},{"pid":"96f1137dbdc87835a3fffef353f5b01dd03a6e36","tid":2499720,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"一名姓葉分店經理阻止眾人叫口號及展示橫額，經理又自稱，已自願接種兩劑疫苗，「我哋咁做法都係為國家、為香港、為自己飯碗、為老闆」，故不覺得有問題，惟被在場人士質疑「為飯碗」難稱作自願<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeAo6EDBps23eKxazd44srG86ksmXs1ShU5MxpNj9mVnS?filename=fS7wyCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfS7wyCA.jpg&h=2a3de0e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f078b7ff61113cec5ae17bfeb406806db0385afb","tid":2499720,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:40:47.000Z","msg":"執剩佢一間都唔會幫襯佢"},{"pid":"c7a2bc95bbc5da3fd89673320670803b1dff628b","tid":2499720,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"你為國家番酒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071c993740bc3c5b821d85b740c8545268ae5a71","tid":2499720,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"等睇又唔關疫苗事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fa017fc3dc72d60f7b9e582fd303c37a51a580","tid":2499720,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"為國家就應該唔洗出糧俾佢<br />\n兼上繳全部身家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e612d2e0688dd9af7e44c62c8877da747b6849","tid":2499720,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"為國家犧牲"},{"pid":"a88277655e82b19aee6b8d00711eb7b89ffc2b2e","tid":2499720,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQgiQ9VCn9pu7hXdc2Ui6eTS64j5uCKHeAanFmSYgRFGS?filename=9EcksMq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EcksMq.gif&h=e72e489d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmamfPoU7kSWQamBsa61sQLsePhcdCnKVmZLcNacLXRWdY?filename=ET5Rzrs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FET5Rzrs.gif&h=81fcbc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcr8wXPbBqvpy3dTHSsJ84Jyz9fvq5vrLmD1sZkyQSRWP?filename=whTDer0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwhTDer0.gif&h=d2845922&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b1315494d202b3ee3e78f3f07f139d5aa4b7c3d","tid":2499720,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"講得出為國家一定係弱智藍狗"}]}